data.description: In the charming, established neighborhood of Pierpont in West Ashley, this spacious home on a generous corner double lot is on the market for the first time since its construction in 1962. The home was lovingly cared for by the original owners over the years, and is now ready for a new family to embellish with their own style and personality. With plenty of room for expansion, gardening, and outdoor entertainment, there are numerous customization options including room additions or a reversion of the enclosed garage. Adorned with many of its original midcentury elements, this home exudes a warmth and character that is immediately inviting. 2016 Dogwood Road is a canvas awaiting your personal touch, a place where memories have been made and where new ones are waiting to be created.
